This script shall be a simple wrapper from a WMS to TMS.

You can add this layer to OpenLayers as:

    var layer = new OpenLayers.Layer.OSM(
            "Test Layer",
	    "http://example.com/wms_to_tms/?foo=bar&path=${z}/${x}/${y}.png",
	    { numZoomLevels: 19, isBaseLayer: false });
    map.addLayer(layer);

All parameters (save path) will be passed to the WMS.
